name: F.A.J. Tech. Home Entertainment early test demo (teaser Game)
name_original: F.A.J. Tech. Home Entertainment early test demo (teaser Game)
description:
I know you're very busy, but before I get out of work, would you test this demo

Normally, I would have tested this demo, but the management wants to release this game in a month, 

and we are still at the very beginning of the game.

                             1984/03/01  from the gaming department Barbara J.
